%F A278024 a(n) = Sum_{k=floor((n+2)/4)..floor(n/2)} Sum_{j=0..k} (-1)^(k-j) * binomial(k-1,k-j) * binomial(2*j+1,n-2*k) * (2*j)! / (2^j*j!). - _Andrew Howroyd_, May 08 2023
